    "narrative_summary": "Archer-Daniels-Midland Company reported second quarter 2023 financial results, with earnings per share of $1.70 and adjusted earnings per share of $1.89. The company highlighted strong performance in Ag Services and Oilseeds, particularly in Brazil, and Carbohydrate Solutions, while Nutrition segment results were significantly lower year-over-year. The company raised its full-year 2023 earnings expectations based on strong first-half results and confidence in second-half performance."
